snippet.title: Amberlynn Reid Is A Serious Problem
snippet.description:
Amberlynn Reid is a weight loss YouTuber known for being exposed and getting in trouble, she started off her weight loss journey in 2013 and has currently gained 200lbs since. Today we will be taking a look at that story and why I think she is putting her fans in danger.
